= Slam Conventions

We do not play two-suit KC.

Our primary KC-asking method is kickback.

In some well defined situations we use plain minorwood or optional
minorwood instead of kickback.

== Minorwood

Applies by an unpassed hand when four of the agreed minor is not
needed as a natural bid:

1. jump to 4m after minor-suit agreement

2. jump from 2m to 4m when 3m is forcing

3. raise of opener's minor-suit jump-rebid

4. self raise to 4m following a minor-suit
_ transfer opposite a 1NT opening

