== Kickback for diamonds when hearts are in focus

The primary issue with kickback is when diamonds are agreed and 4H is
still a possible contract.

4H will be kickback #unless hearts are in focus as a possible contract.#

A major-suit is in focus when one of the following applies:

["lowerroman"]
. it was rebid directly after diamond agreement
. delayed support was given directly after diamond agreement
. it was bid on the first round

=== Diamonds agreed, hearts in focus, at 3D

4D is not a jump, so not minorwood.

A jump to 4H is kickback.

