=== Diamonds agreed and we are at the 4-level

If diamonds are agreed and we are at 4C or 4D, then one of 4H or 4S by
an unlimited hand must be kickback for diamonds.

If diamonds were _reaffirmed_ following a 3M bid, then there is
nothing to resolve.  4H is kickback.

Otherwise, if a major was bid on the first round then it is _in focus_
and the other major is KC asking in {D}.

